Gibson Capital, LLCNew Purchases: IWD ,Added Positions: DSI , IJR , IAU, AAPL, BRK.B,Reduced Positions:VNQI, VV, RWX, GLD, IWV, VOO, EEM, EFA, IJH,For the details of Gibson Capital, LLC's stock buys and sells, go to http://www.gurufocus.com/StockBuy.php?GuruName=Gibson+Capital%2C+LLCThese are the top 5 holdings of Gibson Capital, LLCVanguard Total Stock Market ( VTI ) - 946,411 shares, 39.25% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 0.93%Vanguard REIT ETF - DNQ ( VNQ ) - 839,765 shares, 23.68% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 0.71%iShares TIPS Bond ( TIP ) - 224,050 shares, 8.75% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 0.78%Procter & Gamble Co ( PG ) - 154,136 shares, 4.74% of the total portfolio.Vanguard Div Appreciation ETF - DNQ ( VIG ) - 146,945 shares, 4.52% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 0.74%New Purchase: iShares Russell 1000 Value (IWD)Gibson Capital, LLC initiated holdings in iShares Russell 1000 Value. The purchase prices were between $111.95 and $118.42, with an estimated average price of $114.65. The stock is now traded at around $114.61. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.07%. The holdings were 1,746 shares as of 2017-03-31.Added: iShares Core S&P Small-Cap (IJR)Gibson Capital, LLC added to the holdings in iShares Core S&P Small-Cap by 125.02%. The purchase prices were between $67.46 and $140.6, with an estimated average price of $82.1. The stock is now traded at around $67.84. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.06%. The holdings were 4,793 shares as of 2017-03-31.Added: Apple Inc (AAPL)Gibson Capital, LLC added to the holdings in Apple Inc by 28.45%. The purchase prices were between $116.02 and $144.12, with an estimated average price of $131.71. The stock is now traded at around $143.51. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.03%. The holdings were 3,138 shares as of 2017-03-31.IJR 15-Year Financial DataThe intrinsic value of IJRPeter Lynch Chart of IJRPremium MembersThis art