Company Overview of Gibson Capital, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Gibson Capital, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, trusts, estates, foundations, retirement plans, and corporations and other businesses. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets of United States. The firm uses a combination of quantitative and qualitative analysis to make its investments. It conducts in-house research to make its investments. Gibson Capital, LLC was founded in 1989 and is based in Wexford, Pennsylvania.


6600 Brooktree Court.Suite 2200Wexford, PA 15090United StatesFounded in 1989



